    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_54_1866-1911",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "1866-1911",
      "markText": "我们不希望这种痛苦再让我们的孩子、孙子这一代承受，2300万的（台湾人）不要再受这个痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 735,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=1866&rangeEnd=1911",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=1866&rangeEnd=1911"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_13_4403-4496",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4403-4496",
      "markText": "陈诚认为，国民党之所以在大陆失败，就是失去了人民特别是农民的支持，而失去农民支持的根本原因是国民党土地政策的失败。为了避免在台湾出现类似的情况，就必须在台湾进行土地改革，保证农民的生活。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4403&rangeEnd=4496",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4403&rangeEnd=4496"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_22_3046-3076",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "3046-3076",
      "markText": "后来蒋介石自己也承认，说这是他在国共大战里头最大的一次错误。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3046&rangeEnd=3076",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3046&rangeEnd=3076"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_3_3539-3635",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3539-3635",
      "markText": "老先生办公的时候要回形针，但他不叫回形针，叫“插销”。一般人想应该是门上那个插销吧，结果错了。老先生又讲“拿绢头”，绢头是什么？上海人讲手帕，宁波人才讲绢头。一个武官去拿什么？去拿了块砖头来。",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3539&rangeEnd=3635",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3539&rangeEnd=3635"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_6_881-948",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "881-948",
      "markText": "从此，台湾进入长达38年的“戒严时期”，被白色恐怖所笼罩，甚至达到了只要有人敢讲“政府”不好，就有可能会失踪，要么进监狱，要么被枪毙。",
      "totalCount": 372,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=881&rangeEnd=948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=881&rangeEnd=948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_38_2417-2483",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "2417-2483",
      "markText": "我们孔家本来很有钱，为了国民革命事业，父亲还捐了不少钱。他当财政部长时，财政收入创下国府执政的新高纪录，他如果是个贪官污吏，可能吗？",
      "totalCount": 350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2417&rangeEnd=2483",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2417&rangeEnd=2483"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_40_1533-1609",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "1533-1609",
      "markText": "1979年1月，中华人民共和国与美国正式建立外交关系，中华人民共和国国防部长徐向前发表《停止炮击大、小金门等岛屿》的声明，双方历时21年的炮击正式结束。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1533&rangeEnd=1609",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1533&rangeEnd=1609"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_39_1960-2042",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "1960-2042",
      "markText": "因为这层特殊的关系，本来就霸道的孔令伟行事更加肆无忌惮。在南京的时候，有一次她开车兜风，因为违反交通规则，被交警训了几句，她一怒之下，竟然拔出手枪，将交警当场击毙。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=1960&rangeEnd=2042",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=1960&rangeEnd=2042"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_4_1350-1367",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1350-1367",
      "markText": "在宋美龄的斡旋下，西安事变和平解决",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1350&rangeEnd=1367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1350&rangeEnd=1367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_14_3504-3524",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "3504-3524",
      "markText": "第一个在地方上要有声望，第二个是要孝顺。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=3504&rangeEnd=3524",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=3504&rangeEnd=3524"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_3_3747-3808",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3747-3808",
      "markText": "结果有一次山东武官听成了“枪毙”，吓得发抖发慌，怎么这样就要被枪毙？副官跟他讲，我像你这样子“枪毙”，早就被枪毙十几次了。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3747&rangeEnd=3808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3747&rangeEnd=3808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_5_3851-3880",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3851-3880",
      "markText": "他就说怎么样好怎么样好。老先生很高兴，老人家就喜欢听好的。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3851&rangeEnd=3880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3851&rangeEnd=3880"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_4_3272-3322",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3272-3322",
      "markText": "名侍卫见到蒋介石以后，毕恭毕敬地说：“先生，达令让我告诉您……”蒋介石听到后，简直不敢相信自己的耳朵",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3272&rangeEnd=3322",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3272&rangeEnd=3322"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_21_3900-3973",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "3900-3973",
      "markText": "我们坐在汽车里一路颠簸前行，远处还不时传来轰隆的炮火声，父亲突然扯开嗓门唱起了岳飞的《满江红》：“怒发冲冠，凭栏处……”我们受到感染，一路跟着唱。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3900&rangeEnd=3973",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3900&rangeEnd=3973"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_12_456-534",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "456-534",
      "markText": "蒋介石用人的时候有三条不成文的规定，第一是重用黄埔系出身的军人，因为蒋介石自己就是靠黄埔系起家的；第二是重用浙江的同乡；第三是重用对蒋介石个人十分忠诚的人。",
      "totalCount": 319,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=456&rangeEnd=534",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=456&rangeEnd=534"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_21_979-1053",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "979-1053",
      "markText": "。鉴于武器装备敌强我弱，以正规战与敌人硬拼难以持久，白崇禧提出以游击战配合正规战，积小胜为大胜，以空间换时间的作战指导思想。这些建议都被蒋介石采纳。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=979&rangeEnd=1053",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=979&rangeEnd=1053"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_4_2066-2149",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2066-2149",
      "markText": "访问期间，美国总统罗斯福发来一份电报，美国将为中国提供贷款。随后，英国也宣布为中国提供贷款。经过多次协商后，美国和英国还自愿放弃了清末不平等条约所给予他们的治外法权。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2066&rangeEnd=2149",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2066&rangeEnd=2149"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_51_7206-7256",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "7206-7256",
      "markText": "陈明忠：这个本来挺好的，结果后来大陆人民公社开始了，他说我们搞人民公社，就受到处罚了。",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=7206&rangeEnd=7256",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=7206&rangeEnd=7256"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_27_396-420",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "396-420",
      "markText": "她看到经国先生并无纯中国血统的孩子，自愿以身相许",
      "totalCount": 276,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924944&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=396&rangeEnd=420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/45f320105e1d1045fbdb873?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=396&rangeEnd=420"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924944_6_3615-3689",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3615-3689",
      "markText": "此事最终的解决办法是台湾当局向美方道歉、赔偿，同时蒋介石下令撤除“卫戍司令”黄珍吾、“宪兵司令”刘炜和“警务处处长”乐干的职务。这样风波才慢慢平息。",
